name: Darth Maul's Demise
Lore: 'Despite coming face to face with the first Sith to be seen in a millennia, the young Padawan was still a force to be reckoned with.',
Text: 'If your [Episode I] Jedi just defeated Maul in lightsaber combat, draw destiny. Add 2 if Qui-Gon out of play. If total > 6, place Maul out of play and you may search your Lost Pile and take any one card into hand. (Immune to Sense.)',
